OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Police chiefs in England and Wales have
OL,6, pledged to send an officer to every    
OL,7, single burgled home.                   
OL,9,FThe pledge commits forces to sending an
OL,10,Fofficer to investigate every report of 
OL,11,Fhome burglary, regardless of location  
OL,12,Fand what has been stolen.              
OL,14,FAll 43 forces agreed to the commitment 
OL,15,Fat last week's meeting of the National 
OL,16,FPolice Chiefs' Council, its chairman   
OL,17,Fwrote in the Daily Mail.               
OL,19,FMartin Hewitt said the move was aimed  
OL,20,Fat giving people "peace of mind".      
